name: Low Spur
description:
Introduction

Nice 17' entry DC

The skilled can DC AND reclimb the 3 stage 80' rap with no rope. If not confident, bring a rope and ascending gear and know how to use it (anchor is a large chockstone) You can continue down to an obvious drop/DC into a likely pool. But below this there is nothing of note. Turn back BEFORE committing to this drop (although it is possible to also reclimb this drop)

Approach

Descent

Exit

Red tape
